      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The Lord gives righteousness and justice to all who are treated unfairly. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The Lord gives righteousness and justice to all who are treated unfairly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He revealed his character to Moses and his deeds to the people of Israel. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He revealed his character to Moses and his deeds to the people of Israel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The Lord is compassionate and merciful, slow to get angry and filled with unfailing love. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The Lord is compassionate and merciful, slow to get angry and filled with unfailing love."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He will not constantly accuse us, nor remain angry forever. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He will not constantly accuse us, nor remain angry forever."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He does not punish us for all our sins; he does not deal harshly with us, as we deserve. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He does not punish us for all our sins; he does not deal harshly with us, as we deserve."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For his unfailing love toward those who fear him is as great as the height of the heavens above the earth. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For his unfailing love toward those who fear him is as great as the height of the heavens above the earth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He has removed our sins as far from us as the east is from the west. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He has removed our sins as far from us as the east is from the west."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The Lord is like a father to his children, tender and compassionate to those who fear him. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The Lord is like a father to his children, tender and compassionate to those who fear him."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For he knows how weak we are; he remembers we are only dust. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For he knows how weak we are; he remembers we are only dust."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our days on earth are like grass; like wildflowers, we bloom and die. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our days on earth are like grass; like wildflowers, we bloom and die."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The wind blows, and we are gone— as though we had never been here. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The wind blows, and we are gone— as though we had never been here."
